GREEN EMERALD HOMES, LLC, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
U.S. BANK NATIONAL ASSOC., as Trustee, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0375 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. July 30, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellee's unopposed motion to retake jurisdiction and dismiss appeal as moot is granted. This appeal is dismissed.

MORRIS, SLEET, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
